      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "arrival",
      "speaker": "Gustave"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch32-03",
      "text": "Le savant regarde.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "arrival",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch32-04",
      "text": "L'Empereur arrive au labo pour la visite.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "arrival",
      "speaker": "Gustave"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch32-05",
      "text": "Gustave attend Sa Majesté car la visite est aujourd'hui.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "arrival",
      "speaker": "Gustave"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch32-06",
      "text": "Bonsoir, Majesté !",
      "imagePrompt": "Inside the candlelit 1870 laboratory, Gustave Franklin bows before Napoleon III, both figures facing the viewer. A hand extended in formal greeting is the focal point, brass instruments gleaming on shelves behind them. Medium shot, eye-level. Warm candlelight bathes the scene, respectful and ceremonial mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "greeting",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch32-07",
      "text": "La visite est aujourd'hui.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "greeting",
      "speaker": "Gustave"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch32-08",
      "text": "On dit bonsoir.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "greeting",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch32-09",
      "text": "Aujourd'hui, c'est le jour.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "greeting",
      "speaker": "Gustave"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch32-10",
      "text": "Le savant regarde l'Empereur.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "greeting",
      "speaker": "Gustave"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch32-11",
      "text": "Cinq ans, dit l'Empereur.",
      "imagePrompt": "In the 1870 laboratory, Napoleon III faces the viewer holding up five fingers sternly, Gustave Franklin standing beside the massive brass reactor. The five raised fingers are the focal point. Medium shot, eye-level. Gas lamps illuminate the tense exchange, impatient and demanding mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "five_years",
      "speaker": "Gustave"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch32-12",
      "text": "Il faut poursuivre le travail.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "five_years",
      "speaker": "Gustave"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch32-13",
      "text": "Il y a cinq ans de travail.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "five_years",
      "speaker": "Gustave"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch32-14",
      "text": "On poursuit la visite.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "five_years",
      "speaker": "Gustave"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch32-15",
      "text": "Sa Majesté regarde le réacteur.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "five_years",
      "speaker": "Gustave"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch32-16",
      "text": "C'est une foire !",
      "imagePrompt": "In the chaotic 1870 laboratory, Napoleon III gestures angrily at the disarray facing the viewer, Gustave flinching beside a shuddering brass device about to malfunction. Scattered tools and toppled beakers fill the cluttered workbench. Medium shot, eye-level. Flickering gas lamps cast unsteady light, alarmed and chaotic mood.",
      "readings": [],
